proof_script:
lemma crel_vs_bind_eq: "\<lbrakk>crel_vs (=) v s; crel_vs R (f v) (sf v)\<rbrakk> \<Longrightarrow> crel_vs R (f v) (s \<bind> sf)"
unfolding crel_vs_def
apply clarsimp
subgoal for heap
unfolding bind_def
by (cases "execute s heap") auto
done
